# Implementation Plan - Update Jin Hong M&E Website to v4.0 Standards

Update the existing `jin-hong-me-html-v2` website to comply with the latest global agent automation protocols (v4.0). This includes adding missing UI components, enhancing animations, and ensuring structural consistency across all pages.

## Proposed Changes

### Global Styles and Interactions
#### [MODIFY] [global.css](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/css/global.css)
- Add styles for the Scroll-to-Top button (45x45px, 8px radius).
- Add helper classes for the "Page Introduction" section (flex/grid alternating layout).
- Ensure body has appropriate top-offset or padding to prevent header overlap if needed.

#### [MODIFY] [main.js](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/js/main.js) (or create if missing)
- Implement `IntersectionObserver` for animated number counters.
- Implement Scroll-to-Top button logic:
    - Fades in when scrolling down.
    - Triggers smooth scroll to top.
    - Animates the WhatsApp button (`.float-wa`) upward by 60px when the Scroll-to-Top button appears to prevent collision.

### Homepage Enhancements
