## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- N/A (Static HTML project)

### Manual Verification
1.  **Scroll Interaction**: Scroll down [index.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/index.html) and verify the Scroll-to-Top button fades in and the WhatsApp button moves up.
2.  **Stat Counters**: Verify numbers in the stats ribbon animate from 0 to their values when scrolled into view.
3.  **Link Integrity**: Click every link in the header and footer to ensure no 404s.
4.  **Responsive Check**: Verify the Scroll-to-Top and WhatsApp buttons do not collide on mobile screens.
5.  **Contrast**: Check text readability on all sections using browser dev tools.
